item.title: HTB - TheNotebook
item.description: TheNotebook ![TheNotebook]/images/htb-thenotebook/thenotebook.png) Contents Write Up Recon Credentials Notes Write Up Two open ports, 22 and 80, one filtered port 10010. Pulling up the website takes us to a notebook page with a register and login link. Let’s look around. ![Welcome Page]/images/htb-thenotebook/thenotebook1.png) The register page lets you sign up without verification. I made a user test1 : password1. The log in page provides error messages that let you verify if a user exists, “admin” exists.
